                "value": 0.884
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Isotopically enriched Te-122",
                "deposited on Ti foil and covered with thin Al",
                "foil (10 micron, Goodfellow).",
                "Te-122 sample thickness 6.0 to 10 mg/cm2.",
                "Composition of target materials in %:",
                "Te-120  <   0.04",
                "Te-122      88.4   +- 0.5",
                "Te-123      1.82",
                "Te-124      1.84",
                "Te-125      1.4",
                "Te-126      2.31",
                "Te-128      2.22",
                "Te-130      2.01"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "STTA",
                "GSPEC",
                "BCINT",
                "MOSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Two stacks each containing 5 sandwiched samples were",
                "irradiated for 1 hour with 10 MeV primary energy at",
                "50 nA beam intensity and one stack with ten sandwiched",
                "samples was irradiated for 1 hour with 21.2 MeV primary",
                "energy at 75 nA deuteron beam.",
                "The beam current was also measured via charge",
                "collection in a Faraday-cup."
              ]
            }
          ],
